<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哞！哞！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>曼先生听到他家的牛在田里大声叫着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他连忙跑出门，看到有个东西闪着火光快速地飞过天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39938</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个东西直接冲向了他的农场。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊，不好了！”曼先生惊慌大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃！”杰克厌烦地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55421</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天午饭是牛肉酱面包。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是美罗城小学的星期一早晨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>学生们正准备去上课。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67000</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我最讨厌牛肉酱面包了。” 玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“又恶心，酱汁又滴得到处都是。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要是火箭女孩儿在就好了。”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她一定可以把我们从牛肉酱面包解救出来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没错，火箭女孩儿无所不能。”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿是美罗城最厉害的超人。”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她会飞，力气也很大，还能从眼睛里射出激光呢！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另外，她还有许多其他的超能力！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“上个星期，她成功阻止了一个想要踏平我们学校的大怪物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有一次，火箭女孩儿打败了巨型机器人，保护了美罗城。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“记得上次月球人打算炸毁地球吗？”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿飞到月球，一下子摧毁了他们的地球炸弹呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们总是在说火箭女孩儿。” 罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是她也并不完美，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我觉得她也无法从牛肉酱面包日中解救出我们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在开玩笑吗？”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“罗西，我看你一定是在嫉妒她。”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嫉妒？”罗西反问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162993</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊。” 特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为每次火箭女孩儿出现，你都不在，所以你很嫉妒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说不定，你还在心里偷偷希望你就是火箭女孩儿呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我？火箭女孩儿？”罗西笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是个荒唐的想法！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，罗西的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>手表的声音设得非常小，只有罗西才可以听到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不想再跟你们说关于火箭女孩儿的事了。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去看看潘校长有没有需要我帮忙的地方。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西走到空无一人的走廊，确认周围没有人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她按下了手表上的一个按钮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个小小屏幕亮了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美罗城的市长布洛姆出现在屏幕上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看上去并不开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“出什么事了，市长？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个奇怪的东西降落在曼先生的农场里。”市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们觉得可能是一艘宇宙飞船。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238827</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“宇宙飞船？外星人乘坐的宇宙飞船？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238828</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们还无法确定。”布洛姆市长说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不管它是什么东西，我们都需要调查清楚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我已经跟潘校长说好了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她说你可以离开学校，去解决这件事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257478</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就靠你了，火箭女孩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我这就出发。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>